analysisPopulations.name: Full Analysis Set
analysisPopulations.text: The Full Analysis Set (FAS) consists of all subjects who receive any ABBV-951 infusion and have a baseline and treatment observation for at least 1 efficacy outcome measure.
analysisPopulations.label: FAS
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: The Full Analysis Set (FAS) consists of all subjects who receive any ABBV-951 infusion and have a baseline and treatment observation for at least 1 efficacy outcome measure.
analysisPopulations.criteria: Received any ABBV-951 infusion AND has baseline observation AND has treatment observation for >= 1 efficacy outcome measure

analysisPopulations.name: Treatment Naive Analysis Set
analysisPopulations.text: The Treatment Naive Analysis Set (TNAS) consists of all subjects in the FAS who have the initial exposure to ABBV-951 in Study M15-741, i.e., subjects who had received ABBV-951 in another study prior to participating in Study M15-741 are excluded from the TNAS.
analysisPopulations.label: TNAS
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: The Treatment Naive Analysis Set (TNAS) consists of all subjects in the FAS who have the initial exposure to ABBV-951 in Study M15-741, i.e., subjects who had received ABBV-951 in another study prior to participating in Study M15-741 are excluded from the TNAS.
analysisPopulations.criteria: Included in FAS AND initial exposure to ABBV-951 occurred in Study M15-741 (no prior ABBV-951 in other studies)

analysisPopulations.name: Safety Analysis Set
analysisPopulations.text: The Safety Analysis Set consists of all subjects who receive any ABBV-951 infusion.
analysisPopulations.label: Safety
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: The Safety Analysis Set consists of all subjects who receive any ABBV-951 infusion.

characteristics.name: Race
characteristics.description: White, Black or African American, Asian, American Indian or Alaska Native, Native Hawaiian or Other pacific islander
